quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  54,23,Achina Samuda ŵaakaaniile akutetela
  54,24,"Ni ŵatite: “Ana mundu jwakuumila mwetuwe jumpepe ni tunkuyeje? Chisimu uwwe pa jele ndemajo chituŵe mu kupotela ni masoka.”"
  54,25,"“Ana chikumbusyo chipelecheedwe kukwakwe (Swaleh jikape) sikati jetu? (Ngwamba), nambo jwalakwe ni jwaunami kusyene, (soni) jwakulikulungusya.”"
  54,26,"Tachimanyilila malaŵi kuti ana nduni jwali jwaunami kusyene, (soni) jwakulikulungusya"
  54,27,"(Twansalile Swaleh kuti): “Chisimu Uwwe tukutumisya ngamiya jekongwe kuŵa mayeso kukwao, basi mwajembechelani ni mpilile.”"
  54,28,"“Ni mwatagulile yanti mesi gagaŵiidwe sikati jao (ni ngamiya, lisiku amweje ŵandu, lisiku line jimweje ngamiya), kumwa kulikose akuŵichilileje (jwakukum’bandika).”"
  54,29,Nambo ŵam’bilasile n’jao (Qudâr bin Sâlif juŵaliji jwakusakalilwa nnope) ni jwajigele (upanga) ni jwajiuleje (ngamiya jila)
  54,30,Ana ilagasyo Yangu yaliji uli kwisa soni itetelo Yangu
  54,31,"Chisimu Uwwe twatumichisye ŵanganyao n’gumilo umpepe, basi niŵaliji nti chisawu mbelenje sya nkutaŵa lichinga (ni gumuka nikupondedwapondedwa)"
  54,32,"Soni chisimu chene tujijepepesye Qur’an kuti jiŵe chikumbusyo, ana pana ŵaajikumbuchila (nikuliwunda najo)"
  54,33,Ŵandu ŵa Lutwi ŵaakaaniile akutetela
  54,34,"Chisimu Uwwe twatumichisye chimbunga cha sakalawe (syasyajonasile wosope ŵene), ikaŵeje ŵaliŵasa lya Lutwi, twajokwele kumasikusiku"
  54,35,"Kuŵa ukoto wakuuma Kukwetu, iyyoyopeyo niyatukutiji pakun’dipila jwaatogolele"
  54,36,"Soni chisimu jwalakwe (Lutwi) jwaatetele ŵanganyao ilagasyo Yetu, nambo ŵaikaichile itetelo"
  54,37,"Soni chisimu ŵannyenjelele (Lutwi kuti ŵape) achalendo ŵakwe (atende nao matanyula), basi ni twatatalesye meso gao, (ni twasalile kuti): “Pasyani ilagasyo Yangu ni itetelo Yangu.”"
  54,38,Ni yaalaaŵiile ŵanganyao kundaŵi ilagasyo yakutamilichika
  54,39,"(Twasalile kuti): “Pasyani ilagasyo Yangu ni itetelo Yangu.”"
  54,40,"Soni chisimu chene tujijepepesye Qur’an kuti jiŵe chikumbusyo, ana pana ŵaajikumbuchila (nikuliwunda najo)"